### Create a conversation
POST http://localhost:4004/chat/createConversation
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My first chat",
  "agentType": "router"
}

### Send a message (paste conversationId from above response)
POST http://localhost:4004/chat/sendMessage
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conversationId": "PASTE-UUID-HERE",
  "message": "Hello DevPilot!"
}

### List conversations
GET http://localhost:4004/chat/Conversations

### List messages
GET http://localhost:4004/chat/Messages?$expand=conversation